{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"05da7991af","title":"王力给姚登山的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8d1604b93b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":8,"articleId":"05da7991af"}],"tags":[{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"2bffb53b5b","name":"对外关系和政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"fa147b61e7","name":"王力"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f5daa4cfa4","type":"title","text":"王力给姚登山的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"05da7991af"},{"id":"0c294768e2","type":"paragraph","text":"姚登山同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"05da7991af"},{"id":"c374e24ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"我们接到外交部革命造反总部八月五日的一封信，并附了你讲话的一个摘要。这封信和材料，关锋、戚本禹同志和我都看了。我们认为，革命造反总部这封信的精神是不好的，不对头。戚本禹同志讲的几句话，是正确的。你讲的话，也是对的。这些话引起群情激昂，高呼口号，是好事，是革命的景象。这些，为什么一定要加以反对呢？斗争的矛头究竟要指向谁呢？在要陈毅到群众中去检查的问题上，总理同文革小组的同志是一致的，企图从中寻找什么裂痕是徒劳的。现将外交部革命造反总部的信和附件送去。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"05da7991af"},{"id":"4c2a8aa8b4","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"05da7991af"},{"id":"0eabd2f967","type":"paragraph","text":"王力","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"05da7991af"},{"id":"d14efb91cc","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年八月八日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"05da7991af"}],"page":{"id":"e7ca65ad1e","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"05da7991af","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}